      <bioghist>
         
         <head>Biographical Note</head>
         
         <p>James Major Baley (1912-) was a judge on the Court of Appeals in the <date era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1970s</date>.</p>
      
      </bioghist>
      
      <scopecontent>
         
         <head>Collection Overview</head>
         
         <p>This collection consists of official letters, speeches, data concerning party organization, newspaper clippings, printed matter (both from the state Republican Party and the national executive committee), a list of contributors to the state party in <date era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1952</date>, official press releases, and financial records.</p>
      
      </scopecontent>
      
